# Kyrgyz → IPA transliteration rules (ky_ipa.rules)
# Source: Help:IPA/Kyrgyz, rev. 6 Jan 2025.
# Updated 26 Jun 2025 to align 1 : 1 with McCollum (2020) phoneme inventory.
# Lines marked with “►” are new in this revision.

$V = [ɑeiouøyɯ];            # vowel macro: Kyrgyz short vowels

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# /je/ only after another vowel
# McCollum (2020) shows that native Kyrgyz word-initial ‹е/Е› is realised
# as plain [e]; the glide appears only post-vocalically or after ъ/ь which
# are handled elsewhere.
$V } Е > je ;
$V } е > je ;

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# digraph affricates (loans) ►
ДЖ > ʤ ;  дж > ʤ ;          # voiced postal-alveolar affricate

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
